description: Craving some nugs? This one-tray wonder combines crunchy, sticky chicken nuggets with capsicum, broccoli and spring onions for a moreish (and easy) dinner or speedy lunch.
name: Sticky Tempura Nuggets Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 2 spring onions, thinly sliced into rounds

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 220°C/200°C fan-forced. Grease a large baking tray and line with baking paper. Place chicken nuggets, in a single layer, on tray. Bake for 10 minutes.
Drizzle chicken with sweet chilli sauce. Turn to coat. Return to the oven and bake for a further 10 minutes or until golden brown.
Add capsicum and vegetables to the tray. Turn to coat. Bake for a further 5 minutes or until vegetables are tender. Remove from oven. Sprinkle with onion and sesame seeds. Serve.
